# WhisperX model table — covers ASR and alignment models.
#
# This file uses the shared huggingface data table schema.
# The pipeline_tag column distinguishes model types:
#   automatic-speech-recognition | alignment
# The free_tag column is set to "whisperx" for all rows so the XML can
# filter specifically for WhisperX rows in the shared table.
#
# To configure:
# 1. Copy this file to huggingface.loc (removing .sample), or append to an
#    existing huggingface.loc shared with other tools (e.g. Flux)
# 2. Replace /data/db/whisperx_models with the actual root directory
#    created by download_models_3.4.2.py
# 3. Remove rows for models you have not downloaded
#
# Columns:
#   value        : unique row identifier
#   name         : display label shown in Galaxy UI
#   pipeline_tag : automatic-speech-recognition (ASR models) | alignment (forced-alignment models)
#   domain       : whisper size key (automatic-speech-recognition) or BCP-47 language code (alignment)
#   free_tag     : whisperx (used by the tool XML to filter rows)
#   version      : tool version this row belongs to
#   path         : root model directory (containing hub/, nltk_data/, etc.)
#
# Columns: value <TAB> name <TAB> pipeline_tag <TAB> domain <TAB> free_tag <TAB> version <TAB> path
#
# --- version 3.4.2 ---
#
# ── ASR models ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
whisperx_3.4.2_asr_turbo	Turbo (~8x faster than large)	automatic-speech-recognition	turbo	whisperx	3.4.2	/data/db/whisperx_models
whisperx_3.4.2_asr_tiny	Tiny (~10x faster than large)	automatic-speech-recognition	tiny	whisperx	3.4.2	/data/db/whisperx_models
whisperx_3.4.2_asr_base	Base (~7x faster than large)	automatic-speech-recognition	base	whisperx	3.4.2	/data/db/whisperx_models
whisperx_3.4.2_asr_small	Small (~4x faster than large)	automatic-speech-recognition	small	whisperx	3.4.2	/data/db/whisperx_models
whisperx_3.4.2_asr_medium	Medium (~2x faster than large)	automatic-speech-recognition	medium	whisperx	3.4.2	/data/db/whisperx_models
whisperx_3.4.2_asr_large	Large	automatic-speech-recognition	large	whisperx	3.4.2	/data/db/whisperx_models
#
